{"tid":381412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機上演算微積分　經濟學教授被當恐怖份子","createTime":"2017-08-31T02:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:32:46.000Z","uid":16528,"like":125,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a963bb104c6de4a661a29401c1be5678be9ff35","tid":381412,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"美國一名大學經濟學教授，在飛機上演算複雜的數學公式，卻被鄰座一名<span style=\"color: red;\">女乘客</span>懷疑是恐怖份子，遭帶離客機接受盤問。<br />\n賓州大學（University of Pennsylvania）經濟學教授孟思奧（Guido Menzio），原定周四（5日）搭乘美國航空AA3950班機由費城前往雪城（Syracuse），再赴加拿大安大略的皇后大學（Queen&rsquo;s University）參加學術研討。<br />\n他在機位等候起飛時，於座位上演算一條微積分公式，但鄰座一名<span style=\"color: red;\">女乘客完全不認識這些數學符號，以為他在寫恐嚇字條，深感不安。女乘客於是謊稱身體不適要下機，等離開機艙後，她向空服員表示：「覺得孟思奧非常可疑，可能是恐怖份子，希望改搭另一架航班。」</span><br />\n機場為了安全起見，立刻派人將孟思奧帶下機。這名原籍義大利的大學教授得知被人當恐怖份子後，哭笑不得，但他配合調查。雖然孟思奧解釋後，很快就獲准重返客機，但客機仍較原定時間晚了兩個多小時才抵達目的地。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160508/855864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160508%2F855864%2F&d=4dOpNOaat%2FznNFlMgXPY5%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5096e1b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160508/855864/</a>"},{"pid":"7a297240b38ab4c8e2cc2fbc54157e49a6f9723f","tid":381412,"uid":16528,"like":226,"dislike":2,"score":224,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人"},{"pid":"9c71f45fb5b5c2e18b26f2845b9988910444ae94","tid":381412,"uid":59742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b9468aa8b764128a6b5dd9221380ccb1ab311c","tid":381412,"uid":135445,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm